{"tid":566712,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"阿古路輸波打球迷？　英足總或秋後算賬","createTime":"2018-02-20T07:45:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-21T15:16:24.000Z","uid":4661,"like":40,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"ff33fbd1f1bd59f4d5e2477094e5d0b159d0fce7","tid":566712,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T07:45:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180220/large/1519082679_bc3d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180220%2Flarge%2F1519082679_bc3d.jpg&h=c11e39f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180220/large/1519082681_8249.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180220%2Flarge%2F1519082681_8249.jpg&h=ab0cbd6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180220/large/1519082686_f126.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180220%2Flarge%2F1519082686_f126.jpg&h=bdba9d35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n曼城周一晚在英格蘭足總盃第5圈作客以0:1不敵英甲球隊韋根出局，季內成為四冠王的美夢幻滅。禍不單行的是，曼城前鋒阿古路賽後牽涉在與主隊球迷的衝突當中，更被電視鏡頭捕捉到疑似推撞，或是出手打韋根球迷，相信英格蘭足總很有可能會作出研訊。<br />\n<br />\n根據英國《BBC》的電視畫面，韋根球迷在完場後衝入球場慶祝，期間曼城前鋒阿古路似乎推撞，或是出手打一名走近自己身邊的韋根球迷，暫時未知這位阿根廷射手是否在受到球迷的挑釁下才有所動作。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，當曼城左閘戴爾夫在上半場補時階段被逐離場後，曼城領隊哥迪奧拿和韋根主帥保羅曲克在場邊發生激烈爭執，事件在半場兩隊步入更衣室期間仍然繼續。韋根主場內的球員通道鏡頭亦拍攝到事發經過，但哥帥賽後淡然表示「半場時甚麼事情都沒有發生」，拒絕評論當時的情況。"},{"pid":"ecc183776c44f3ad81f46e4aab8562f115c10a81","tid":566712,"uid":131369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T07:46:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf50b1ed3ee5d66de57aeba482afb615ed57b0df","tid":566712,"uid":36138,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T07:47:25.000Z","msg":"打狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb4ea67312e74a34ca91f95ddbe7f85199e34d88","tid":566712,"uid":3167,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T07:48:07.000Z","msg":"曼狗咬人啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e054da4ea2e99701b472cd15afcf28c11fd7963","tid":566712,"uid":119729,"like":61,"dislike":1,"score":60,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T07:48:49.000Z","msg":"真人同會然都是辣殺"},{"pid":"1c014d2f74639763711d08663550615c2fde5bf2","tid":566712,"uid":33719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T07:49:57.000Z","msg":"快d加盟熱狗啦"},{"pid":"c7f1ad0eecb2857d8b545408d8ab883ab11dc769","tid":566712,"uid":36138,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1c014d2f74639763711d08663550615c2fde5bf2","tid":566712,"uid":33719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T07:49:57.000Z","msg":"快d加盟熱狗啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T07:55:21.000Z","msg":"一齊剷鳩車狗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7ae1344b5319cf64edf69de4014b133e6b884a4","tid":566712,"uid":31744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e054da4ea2e99701b472cd15afcf28c11fd7963","tid":566712,"uid":119729,"like":61,"dislike":1,"score":60,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T07:48:49.000Z","msg":"真人同會然都是辣殺"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T07:59:16.000Z","msg":"Ching 講得好！"},{"pid":"d76e047e6fa2ebfe835913759c68bf74ce60f749","tid":566712,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T08:11:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img s